name: Gucci
description: Gucci is an Italian luxury brand known for its fashion-forward designs and luxury goods.

name: Chanel
description: Chanel is a French high fashion house that focuses on women's ready-to-wear clothes, luxury goods, and accessories.

name: Louis Vuitton
description: Louis Vuitton is a French fashion house and luxury goods company founded in 1854.

name: Prada
description: Prada is an Italian luxury fashion house known for its leather handbags, ready-to-wear, shoes, and accessories.

name: Versace
description: Versace is an Italian luxury fashion company and trade name founded by Gianni Versace, producing accessories, fragrances, and home furnishings.

name: Hermès
description: Hermès is a French high fashion luxury goods manufacturer specializing in leather, lifestyle accessories, home furnishings, perfumery, jewelry, watches, and ready-to-wear.

name: Dior
description: Dior is a French luxury goods company known for haute couture, leather goods, fashion accessories, and fragrances.

name: Balenciaga
description: Balenciaga is a luxury fashion house founded in Spain, known for its innovative and modernist designs.

name: Burberry
description: Burberry is a British luxury fashion brand, known for its trench coats, distinctive check pattern, and outdoor apparel.

name: Fendi
description: Fendi is an Italian luxury fashion house best known for its leather goods, ready-to-wear, and accessories.
